messages.message: Who would be the best person to bring into a demo about how you can write notebooks, scritps, put them into flows/refiner programs, and also making a metaflow that has multiple UDF's. A customer (Flexport) is really interested in this feature. They are tired of managing flows and notebooks on their own homemade thing.
@Matt which SE are you working with on Flexport?
Just got a call with them so I need to fill out the page, but wanted to gauge a bit more value before bringing in a SE. If it doesn't meet our bare requirements I don't want to waste time
